videos.headline: UNC's Corrales Mosses defender for TD
videos.description: North Carolina QB Sam Howell throws to the end zone and Beau Corrales rises over his defender to win the jump ball for the 21-yard score.

videos.headline: Pitt airs it out for 74-yard TD
videos.description: Pittsburgh QB Kenny Pickett goes deep to connect with Shocky Jacques-Louis for a 74-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: UNC ties game on Howell's 3rd TD
videos.description: North Carolina QB Sam Howell hits Dazz Newsome in stride for a 34-yard score, tying the game at 24.
